        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Expedita
          aspernatur impedit ea dolore ducimus eius architecto esse sint dolor
          quia!
        </p>
        <a
          href="/ice-cream"
          class="mt-5 bg-accent text-white font-bold rounded-3xl py-4 px-12 inline-block leading-none"
          >Learn More About Our Story</a
        >
      </div>
      <Image
        class="rounded-lg"
        height={500}
        src={import("@img/home/wayne.jpg")}
        alt="wayne ferris of the roxbury market"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
